title: United Kingdom Imports of Paper & Paperboard & Related Articles
description: Imports of Paper & Paperboard & Related Articles in the United Kingdom decreased to 655.37 GBP Million in September from 684.81 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Paper & Paperboard & Related Articles in the United Kingdom averaged 468.91 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 1937.50 GBP Million in March of 2015 and a record low of 258.99 GBP Million in February of 2022. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Paper & Paperboard & Related Articles.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
